00:00:01.900 --> 00:00:03.740
Welcome to Instant Cooking

00:00:03.740 --> 00:00:06.760
Today I am going to tell  you how to make Double Tadka Daal

00:00:06.760 --> 00:00:10.960
For this we have to take a bowl of Split red gram dal

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:16.140
and pressure cook it with 3 clove of grated garlic

00:00:16.620 --> 00:00:18.600
1/2 tsp of turmeric

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:21.680
and a tsp of coriander seed powder

00:00:21.960 --> 00:00:23.480
And cook it till it cook

00:00:25.040 --> 00:00:25.840
now further

00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:27.800
take another pan

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:32.700
put 2 tsp of oil

00:00:36.080 --> 00:00:40.200
let it heat up , now put 1/2 tsp of mustard seed

00:00:41.080 --> 00:00:42.320
and let it crackle

00:00:43.980 --> 00:00:49.560
once the mustard seed is crackled add 1/2 a tsp of cumin seeds

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:55.580
then add half a inch of grated ginger

00:00:56.740 --> 00:01:02.260
3-4 clove of garlic and cook it for a minute

00:01:03.640 --> 00:01:05.380
now add 2 green chilli

00:01:06.780 --> 00:01:08.840
and one medium size onion

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.560
cook till onion is transparent

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:28.080
now add 1 medium size chopped tomato

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:31.480
toss it up properly

00:01:33.260 --> 00:01:35.160
now add salt to taste

00:01:41.320 --> 00:01:46.400
as soon as tomato is soften add our cooked dal

00:01:48.920 --> 00:01:53.640
add water in it to make a proper consistency

00:01:55.480 --> 00:01:56.760
cook it for a minute

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:02.360
now add coriander leave to garnish

00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:07.400
remove it from gas &amp; shift it to a bowl

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.860
now take a small tadka pan

00:02:10.900 --> 00:02:15.220
add 2 tsp of clarified butter or Ghee

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:18.760
add 1/2 a tsp of cumin seed

00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:21.620
let them crackle

00:02:22.980 --> 00:02:27.380
and now add 1/2 tsp of red chilli powder

00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:32.480
and put this tadka on our cooked dal

00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:35.660
and our double tadka dal is ready

